        <item>
            <title>Version 1.0.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Mika+Grid 1.0.0</h2>
                <p>Initial release — macOS window snapping menu bar app.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>11 snap actions: halves, quarters, maximize, center, restore</li>
                    <li>Global keyboard shortcuts (Ctrl+Opt + arrow/letter keys)</li>
                    <li>Visual snap grid in menubar popover</li>
                    <li>Multi-monitor support</li>
                    <li>Customizable shortcuts with inline recorder</li>
                    <li>First-launch onboarding with accessibility permission guide</li>
                    <li>Launch at Login</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
